== Prerequisites ==
* Neuvoo overlay

== Variables ==
* /dev/mmcblk0p1 is boot filesystem mounted @ /boot
* /dev/mmcblk0p2 is root filesystem mounted @ /

== Download ==
```bash
emerge -av neuvoo-beagleboard-kernel
```

== Installing ==

''Kernel''
```bash
cp /usr/lib/neuvoo/neuvoo-beagleboard-kernel.bin /boot/uImage
```

''Modules''
```bash
tar -xvjpf /usr/lib/neuvoo/neuvoo-beagleboard-kernel-modules.tar.bz2 -C /
```
